name: Listened to iPhone’s Amazing New Camera, Tesla vs Porsche Round 2, & Google Pixel 4 Leaks

content.html:
Today, we revisit the Tesla vs Porsche Taycan debate by dissecting some laptimes that Tesla put down on an all new Model S model available next year, followed by a deep-dive into how great the iPhone 11 cameras have performed after a week of daily use, followed by an examination of the numerous Google Pixel 4 Leaks to see what we’re excited about in the upcoming phone. Lastly, we wrap it all up with another Listener Q & A!Links from Episode:Waveform Twitter: https://twitter.com/WVFRM 1 Password: https://1password.com/mkbhd Phil Defranco Podcast: https://bit.ly/2kSki2X Jon Rettinger Apple Bankrupt Video: https://bit.ly/2m3deR8 Tesla at Nurburgring: https://bit.ly/2mnxsoZ Pixel 4 Leaks: https://bit.ly/2kAHraa OnePlus 7T Leaks: https://bit.ly/2kJVI4r Learn more about your ad choices.
